@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp(0.52) - wp.cos((v0 + 0.21 + v0 + 0.89)))
    v0 = wp.abs((0.28 + (v0 + 0.57 / tmp + 0.19)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(v2) * 0.42)
    v1 = wp.exp(v0)
    data[tid] = v0
